						<summary>

						<p>Broken pillar behind the Amarēśvara temple.</p>						

						<p>This undated record may be assigned to the 8th century, on the basis of palaeography.</p>						

						<p>It refers to the village Niṭūru and contains the imprecatory portion.</p>						

